        "TileImage": "$($repository 93221913-4b54-4885-8479-2d90814c413d).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47,\r\rToday you need to put an end to the Flower cartel. The leader of the cartel, Kenneth Flower, has killed along with his business partners more than a thousand people to obtain the special ingredient for his wine: human blood. Many innocent civilians became a victim of Mr. Flowers wine company. We need to stop them before they kill more innocent civilians.\r\rGood luck, 47",
